item.title: Skyjacks: Episode 196
item.description: The Uhuru Crew hauls the remainder of the peat aboard and scrambles to heat the furnaces and get the ship aloft. However, The Cutting Stone closes in around them. The crew faces more rolls on the Uhuru Death chart than they ever have before. It is a race to take to the air before they lose their comrades and the captian's council is en route but physically unable to help. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/OSPN2193291028
